    "## If You Only Remember One Thing": "→ anchor (memory anchor callout)",
    "## Analogy": "→ anchor (analogy callout)",
    "## Visual Primitive": "→ visual (visualType: 'diagram', prompt extracted)",
    "## Concept-Specific Mini-Quiz Stems": "→ EXCLUDED from LearningModule.sections[] (feeds C7 authoring instead)",
